---
layout: base
permalink: /about/index.html
title: About
description: "Hello, fellow wanderer. I’m Bryan and this is my blog, a place where I write short status updates about what’s going on in my life, post photos, and occasionally shout into the void."
---

{% set readingPosts = collections.posts | withAnyTagSlugs("books,now-reading") %}
{% set readingPost = readingPosts[0] %}

<article class="content content-page h-entry">
  <header class="post-header">
    <h1 class="content-title">
      <a class="p-name u-url" href="{{ page.url }}">About</a>
    </h1>
  </header>

  <section class="post-full-content">
    <div class="content-body e-content">
      <p>Hello, fellow wanderer. I’m Bryan and this is my blog, a place where I write short status updates about what’s going on in my life, post photos, and occasionally shout into the void.</p>

      <p>I’m an urban planner by profession, having worked in long-range planning, community development, and campus planning for nearly two decades. For better or worse, I spend a lot of time thinking about environmental psychology, urban design, landscape architecture, human geography, and public transportation. If these topics interest you, I also write about urbanism and related things here.</p>

      <p>Growing up in poverty shaped how I see the world. It left me with a deep belief that housing and healthcare are basic rights, and that education and a healthy environment shouldn’t depend on circumstance. I try to put that into practice by volunteering my time with causes that reflect those values.</p>

      <p>At my core, I enjoy creating. Whether that be through writing, making music, practicing photography, gardening, cooking, learning web development, or making home improvements, I like to express myself through making things.</p>

      <p>Originally from the Great Lakes Region, I’ve called the Pacific Northwest home for going on 10 years now. I’m fiercely proud of my Midwest roots and sometimes suffer intense pangs of nostalgia and longings to return, especially after doom scrolling Zillow listings for a bit.</p>

      <p>That said, I do enjoy the climate and landscapes better here on the West Coast. I like to get outdoors with my young family, so there are a lot of photos of our adventures on this site.</p>

      <p>I love sci-fi movies, but I have a terrible memory for titles and names, so don’t ask me which ones I’ve seen or who my favorite actors are. I also like geeking out about guitar gear and recently built my own Telecaster. Speaking of music, you can check out what I’ve been listening to lately here, or my working chronology of live music.</p>

      <p>In 2020, I became an Italian citizen. What started out as a genealogy hobby turned into a decade-long education in Italian bureaucracy. My wife and I sometimes daydream about a part-time life abroad, so I’m interested in connecting with Italians and expats.</p>

      <p>You can reach me by email, follow my RSS feed, or subscribe to the newsletter for this blog.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  {% if readingPost %}
  <section class="section-block">
    <h2 class="section-title">Reading</h2>
    <div class="home-stream">
      {% set post = readingPost %}
      {% set streamImage = post | firstImage %}
      <article class="home-stream-item h-entry">
        {% if streamImage %}
          <a class="home-stream-media u-url" href="{{ post | localPostUrl }}">
            <img class="home-stream-image u-photo" src="{{ streamImage.src }}" alt="{{ streamImage.alt }}" loading="lazy">
          </a>
        {% endif %}
        <div class="home-stream-body e-content">
          {% if post.excerpt %}
            <p>{{ post.excerpt }}</p>
          {% else %}
            <p><a class="p-name u-url" href="{{ post | localPostUrl }}">{{ post.title }}</a></p>
          {% endif %}
          <p class="home-stream-meta">
            <a class="u-url" href="{{ post | localPostUrl }}">
              <time class="dt-published" datetime="{{ post.published_at | htmlDateString }}">{{ post.published_at | dateDisplay }}</time>
            </a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
  {% endif %}
</article>
